:::Hun-Grr/Banzai-Tron/Time Warp:::

::Hun-Grr hears what the creature says::
Hun-Grr: When Hun-Grr want Quintesson's opinion he ask for it.  If 
Decepticons are not on Hun-Grr's side, then they die!
::He sees Blot, Cutthroat and Sinnertwin fighting.  He shoots each of them 
once::
Hun-Grr: SHUT UP!
::He then walks to the front of the base and opens up his comm::
Hun-Grr: This Hun-Grr.  Any Decepticons here?
~~~~~
::Banzai-Tron gets hit dead on by the blue fire.  His body is severely 
charred::
Banzai-Tron: *cough* that.. the... best.. you got?
::He all of a sudden realizes that he is falling.  His flying mechanisms have 
failed and plummets to the ground, in stasis lock::
~~~~~
::Time Warp wakes up from his long sleep::
Time Warp: Hey Airbomber, you up? Because i think that today might just be 
the day we find Infectra.
